data.value:
Author: Dennis Lang 2009 https://landenlabs.com
Credits: This program was based off of code provided by SysInternals.
Description: Monitor Process List and optionally list open handles. Log process and/or handle information to disk file. Display Disk, Drive and File System Statistics. Export and print.
Keyboard: Nothing special
Warning: Under heavy load process and handle list updates maybe slow.
